'''Seasons for Change''' 是一個香港[[另類搖滾|另類搖滾]]樂團，目前和美國獨立音樂廠牌[[Famined_Records|Famined Records]]與香港獨立音樂廠牌簽約[[SEEAHOLE|SEEAHOLE]] <ref>{{Cite web |url = https://noisebarrage.com/2016/07/09/seasons-for-change-sign-with-famined-records-premiere-music-video-for-meteor/ |title = Seasons For Change Sign With Famined Records, Premiere Music Video For “Meteor” |author = Noise Barrage |date = 2016-07-09 |publisher = Noise Barrage |language = en |accessdate = 2017-03-01 |deadurl = yes |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20161221030057/https://noisebarrage.com/2016/07/09/seasons-for-change-sign-with-famined-records-premiere-music-video-for-meteor/ |archivedate = 2016-12-21 }}</ref>。樂團成立時間在2014年，由主音KASA、吉他手Dennis Ho、鼓手Kulo Ming 和貝斯手Wan Tsz Ching 所成立。2015年吉他手Don Chan 的加入，並正式發佈他們的第一首單曲：Rain。歌曲自推出以來己大受好評，所以樂隊於同年正式與澳洲著名搖滾樂隊[[Tonight_Alive|Tonight Alive]] 監製 Dave Petrovic 合作灌錄首張專輯《Timeless Collective》，於2016年11月11日由[[Famined_Records|Famined Records]]及[[Victory_Records|Victory Records]] 發行。樂隊同時活躍於香港、新加坡、台灣多個音樂節，包括Clockenflap <ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.clockenflap.com/content/seasons-change-fri |title = Clockenflap 2019演出陣容 |author = Clockenflap |date = 2019-11-22 |publisher = [[Clockenflap|Clockenflap]] |language = en |accessdate = 2019-11-22 |deadurl = yes |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200229064403/https://www.clockenflap.com/content/seasons-change-fri |archivedate = 2020-02-29 }}</ref>、[[wow_and_flutter|wow and flutter]] <ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.theweekend.hk/articles/seasons-for-change |title = 〖本地薑專欄．音樂． Seasons for Change〗 |author = 明仔 |date = 2019-07-23 |publisher = wow and flutter |language = zh |accessdate = 2019-07-23 |deadurl = yes |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200229064352/https://www.theweekend.hk/articles/seasons-for-change |archivedate = 2020-02-29 }}</ref>、山海屯音樂節、覺醒音樂節、House of Vans等等，並於2018年獲選亞太區Vans MUSICIANS WANTED比賽總冠軍及於同年[[House_of_Vans|House of Vans]]為加洲洛杉磯傳奇嘻哈歌手[[SCHOOLBOY_Q|SCHOOLBOY Q]]作暖場嘉賓<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.vans.com.hk/news/post/vans-2018-musicians-wanted-33264.html |title = 〖VANS 宣布2018年 MUSICIANS WANTED 比賽亞太區總冠軍 |author = Vans APAC |date = 2018-10-25 |publisher = Vans APAC |language = zh |accessdate = 2018-10-25 |deadurl = no |archive-date = 2020-02-29 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200229064355/https://www.vans.com.hk/news/post/vans-2018-musicians-wanted-33264.html }}</ref>。

'''Seasons for Change'''繼2016年推出處女EP《Timeless Collective》後，樂團在2019年推出首張大碟《Petals of Tomorrow》，風格更趨獨特且多元化。融合了Emo, Pop punk, Post-Hardcore的元素，再加上帶日系搖滾的主音旋律，樂隊用獨特的風格唱出情感故事。

